snippet.title: World Map Quiz - grouping mode
snippet.description:
World Map Quiz - grouping mode:
*find all countries in given group
*in case of mistake 5 second of punishment is added to your time
*countries not belonging to the group can be eliminated

How to download the app?

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qbis.guessthecountry

App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/world-map-quiz-qbis-studio/id1338262626
